title: [MEDICAL MARIJUANA] Run From The Cure - The Rick Simpson Story.D
description: One man fights against the absurd stupidity promulgated by government and pharmaceutical companies against a life-saving miracle cure: medical marijuana (aka cannabis, hemp).  From cancer to diabetes to every manner of malady, this film includes testimony from numerous patients -- some of whom were brought back from death&#039;s door by Simpson&#039;s homemade hemp extracts.
